\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces A PSA official eBay listing used during development. One lesson from this listing was that ``In the PSA Vault'' can appear on the listing page even when it is not in the title, so the program checks enriched listing-page evidence instead of relying only on title text.}}{3}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
